You deserve some beauty in your life this lovely Sunday, and very few things are more beautiful than black bodies being graceful. We already shared the story of the Leap of Dance Academy and the great work that Daniel Ajala is doing with these talented kids. And now, well, let’s just enjoy the discipline and grace that is the kids of the Leap of Dance Academy in ballet poses: <img src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Leap-of-Dance-Academy.jpg?ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" />

